   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Voices for Climate Action AMwA Zambia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">AMwA envisions a dignified and equitable feminist society for African women, girls and gender-expansive persons.   AMwA under the Zambia VCA programme will realize this through advocating for Feminist alternatives being adopted as viable sustainable development models and systems at scale for economic and climate justice. For 5 years(2021-2025) AMwA&apos;s activities will be implemented through partnerships with local organizations that include; Zambia Alliance for Women(ZAW), Community Technology Development Trust(CTDT), Women Life Wellness Foundation</narrative>
  </description>
